// README.md
# Paradox - Level Up Your Life

This is a Next.js project for a self-improvement RPG-style app.

## Setup
1. Install dependencies: `npm install`
2. Start the development server: `npm run dev`

## Deployment
- Deploy on [Vercel](https://vercel.com) by linking this repository.
